latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Mithali, who debuted in the game at the young age of 16, is the first woman to complete 20 years in international cricket, the only cricketer to surpass the 7000-run mark in women’s one-day international matches, recipient of the Padma Shri, Dhyan Chand, Khel Ratna, and many international awards. Not only this, but her story has also sparked a revolution with younger talent taking up the game.
Today, we celebrate the woman who built the core of the Indian women’s cricket team brick by brick.

A powerful video, by @lorealparis , Styled by @punya.bh @divyakdsouza.

@mithaliraj Thank you for all your years of sweat and tears, thank you for standing up for yourself and inspiring us all to do so too, and thank you, obviously, for breaking the boundaries.
We love you, Mithali!
